1
00:00:40,040 --> 00:00:41,320
Good thing I reacted quickly

2
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,040
and didn't fall into the Demon King's trap.

3
00:00:43,040 --> 00:00:44,680
Shishi is so drunk.

4
00:00:44,960 --> 00:00:46,360
I can't leave her alone.

5
00:00:47,280 --> 00:00:48,740
I'd better sleep with her.

6
00:00:58,080 --> 00:00:59,940
It seems she's getting in the way.

7
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:02,130
It's better to make her disappear.

8
00:01:04,440 --> 00:01:04,800
No.

9
00:01:05,440 --> 00:01:07,520
The Demon King didn't look well just now.

10
00:01:07,520 --> 00:01:08,520
If he goes crazy

11
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:10,200
and ambushes us in the middle of the night,

12
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:11,730
wouldn't we both be doomed?

13
00:01:14,960 --> 00:01:15,560
Forget it.

14
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:17,280
I'd better...

15
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:26,039
I thought your injuries were quite severe.

16
00:01:26,039 --> 00:01:27,080
You must not have recovered yet.

17
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:28,760
If the Nether Demons attack you tonight,

18
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:29,840
you definitely won't be able to handle it.

19
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,170
I'll keep watch for you.

20
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:34,720
Since you want to protect me,

21
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:36,500
why not come to bed?

22
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:39,340
Wouldn't it be better to protect me closely?

23
00:01:40,479 --> 00:01:41,680
No need to be so close.

24
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:42,920
Under the bed is fine.

25
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,039
Come up.

26
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:47,720
Yes.

27
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:57,880
Your intention to protect that stupid woman is so obvious.

28
00:01:57,880 --> 00:01:59,680
Are you afraid I wouldn't see it?

29
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,560
Or

30
00:02:02,320 --> 00:02:05,380
are you trying to use someone else to do your dirty work?

31
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:08,160
Lu Danyu.

32
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:10,360
You are so interesting.

33
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:12,280
I'm a little reluctant

34
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,920
to sacrifice you to heaven.

35
00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:24,720
Danyu.

36
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:28,240
Danyu.

37
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:37,800
Danyu.

38
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:38,920
Danyu.

39
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:41,120
Danyu,

40
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,040
wake up.

41
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:43,360
Why are you here?

42
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:45,680
Why are you in this beanpole's bed?

43
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:46,440
Danyu.

44
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,600
Beanpole?

45
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:55,320
Danyu,

46
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,520
why are you in Li Yuan's room?

47
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:58,640
Tell me.

48
00:02:58,760 --> 00:02:59,200
Were you...

49
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:00,640
were you coerced?

50
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,040
Lu Danyu,

51
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:06,160
this concerns your reputation.

52
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:08,160
You'd better explain this clearly.

53
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:09,480
Danyu,

54
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:10,400
tell me.

55
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:12,740
You aren't here voluntarily, right?

56
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:15,120
Danyu.

57
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,440
I love him.

58
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:34,000
Lu Danyu,

59
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,560
you are a girl.

60
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,760
No matter how much you love him,

61
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:38,760
you can't do this.

62
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:43,560
Lu Danyu!

63
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:46,760
You...

64
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,520
You love him?

65
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:56,600
I...

66
00:03:57,640 --> 00:03:58,440
Miss,

67
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:01,280
Master is telling you to go home.

68
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,000
Shishi.

69
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:14,320
Come...

70
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,920
Come out and have breakfast.

71
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,620
It's good that he left.

72
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:21,680
Saves me from worrying all day.

73
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:36,800
Danyu.

74
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:38,080
This is so delicious.

75
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:38,880
Have some too.

76
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:54,920
Eat more.

77
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,040
I, Yueqi,

78
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:13,400
fell in love with you at first sight.

79
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:16,200
I hope you

80
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:17,320
can take me in.

81
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:19,760
But

82
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:21,240
I don't take in servant girls.

83
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:21,880
Miss,

84
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,810
are you in some kind of trouble?

85
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:25,520
Miss,

86
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:27,500
do you have any difficulties?

87
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:32,320
My brother already has a fiancée.

88
00:05:32,320 --> 00:05:34,520
Please conduct yourself with dignity.

89
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:45,300
Yueqi apologizes for the intrusion.

90
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:47,260
Yueqi will take leave for now.

91
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:58,680
Danyu,

92
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:00,700
why did you just say

93
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,160
that I have a fiancée?

94
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,420
I don't have a fiancée.

95
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:05,640
If I didn't say that,

96
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:06,770
how would she leave?

97
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:09,000
I see.

98
00:06:09,080 --> 00:06:10,540
Our Danyu is the smartest.

99
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,200
Xiaoxue.

100
00:06:14,840 --> 00:06:15,920
The one just now

101
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,760
was not human.

102
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:19,880
Watch your mouth.

103
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:24,080
No way.

104
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,810
This Yueqi is not human.

105
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,120
Then what is she?

106
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,780
Where are you feeling unwell?

107
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,280
Not exactly.

108
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:34,409
Then why are you suddenly feeling unwell?

109
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:34,840
Then,

110
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:35,760
eat more.

111
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:39,800
Eat more.

112
00:06:41,880 --> 00:06:42,880
Eat more.

113
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:49,680
Senior Brother Luo,

114
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:52,340
the surrounding demonic aura has been cleared.

115
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:55,920
Reporting to Senior Brother.

116
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:56,200
The entire town and surrounding villages have been inspected.

117
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:56,320
The entire town and surrounding villages have been inspected.

118
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:59,200
The entire town and surrounding villages have been inspected.

119
00:06:59,200 --> 00:06:59,840
Senior Brother.

120
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:00,770
Senior Brother.

121
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:04,840
Everyone did a great job.

122
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,160
When we return to the inn later,

123
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,560
everyone get a good rest.

124
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,000
Chunyi.

125
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:11,400
Since the matter has been resolved,

126
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:13,400
why are we still staying here?

127
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:16,890
These are the current orders from the palace.

128
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:19,360
This place is only thirty miles away from the seal.

129
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:21,000
Do you think the demon would be so stupid

130
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,400
as to linger around?

131
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,680
What do you mean?

132
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,080
Nothing.

133
00:07:27,520 --> 00:07:28,480
I just think that

134
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,120
if I were the demon

135
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,640
and I really wanted to run away,

136
00:07:31,640 --> 00:07:33,200
I'd be far from the seal by now.

137
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:34,400
Maybe even back in the netherworld,

138
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:35,120
back in Lanqi.

139
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,180
Junior brother Du,

140
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:40,760
I know you have a problem with the Palace Master sending us here.

141
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:41,360
But we

142
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,880
are just one of the teams.

143
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:46,120
The Palace Master has already set up an inescapable net.

144
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,120
He won't get away.

145
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:48,800
Then won't someone else get all the credit?

146
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,860
Junior brother Du,

147
00:07:50,960 --> 00:07:52,820
the purpose of our Tiandao Palace

148
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,980
is not only to deal with Lanqi Moyuan,

149
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:57,480
but to eliminate all the nether demons.

150
00:07:59,560 --> 00:07:59,920
Yes,

151
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:00,760
senior brother.

152
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:02,160
I was too short-sighted.

153
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,560
Why are you in my room?

154
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:22,000
Don't you adore me?

155
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:24,040
I couldn't wait for you in my room,

156
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,770
so naturally I had to come over.

157
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,210
Why would I be in your place?

158
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,370
Don't you know best?

159
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:31,480
Know?

160
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,200
What do I know?

161
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:35,440
Tell me,

162
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,679
why are you here?

163
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,970
I haven't fully recovered yet.

164
00:08:39,280 --> 00:08:40,480
I'm afraid that at night,

165
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:42,210
Nether Demons might attack me.

166
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:45,040
I need protection.

167
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,580
In your current state,

168
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:50,320
you could beat three Wei Wuzhous.

169
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,200
Get up.

170
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,800
Forget about those Nether Demons.

171
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:54,640
I'm very sleepy.

172
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:55,600
I'm going to sleep.

173
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:57,130
Goodbye, see yourself out.

174
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:10,280
It's clearly a completely different face.

175
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,240
But why

176
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:15,840
can I feel the exact same soul fluctuation?

177
00:09:24,920 --> 00:09:25,780
Daoist Master,

178
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:28,840
have you really

179
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,880
been reincarnated?
